 The phenomenon of "flotillas" began to appear in Mexico 

00:00:13.050 --> 00:00:15.650
 starting from the 1991 eclipse. 

00:00:15.650 --> 00:00:20.210
 He grew up and soon became the cradle 

00:00:20.210 --> 00:00:23.990
 of this phenomenon, that is tens, hundreds and thousands 

00:00:23.990 --> 00:00:26.210
 of spheres that create formations in the sky. 

00:00:27.120 --> 00:00:30.200
 However, this has also been recorded in other countries: recently 

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:33.090
 in Italy, in Milan, Antonio Urzi 

00:00:33.090 --> 00:00:38.030
 in the center he took these exceptional images 

00:00:38.030 --> 00:00:38.830
 which I will show you now. 

00:00:38.830 --> 00:00:42.370
 A few days later, again in September, 

00:00:42.370 --> 00:00:46.260
 Arturo Robles Gil has filmed one of these "flotillas" 

00:00:46.260 --> 00:00:48.360
 at great height above Mexico City 

00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:51.010
 but filmed very well, they are very good images. 

